com.wookler.zconfig.common.events

Class ConfigUpdateBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.events.ConfigUpdateBatch

  • public class ConfigUpdateBatch
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defines a batch of configuration update event. All events in the batch are expected to be for the same configuration and transaction.
